- Background: {{ $('Map Lead Fields').first().json.background }}
- Track Interest: {{ $('Map Lead Fields').first().json.trackInterest }}
- Lead Score: {{ $('Parse AI Score').first().json.score }}
- Lead Tier: {{ $('Parse AI Score').first().json.tier }}
- Score Reason: {{ $('Parse AI Score').first().json.reason }}
- Source: {{ $('Map Lead Fields').first().json.source }}
- Submitted At: {{ $('Map Lead Fields').first().json.submittedAt }}

Generate the brief in this exact format:

LEAD SNAPSHOT
Name, background, track interest, lead score and tier, how they found us.

RECOMMENDED TRACK
Which track to recommend and why based on their background.

LIKELY OBJECTIONS
Top 2-3 objections this lead will probably raise. For each, give the exact response the rep should use.

OPENING ANGLE
The single best opening question to build rapport and diagnose fit fast.

CLOSING STRATEGY
The most effective closing approach for this lead. Which payment option to lead with. What urgency angle to use.
